  "name": "RPlog_The_Bounty_Even_Hunters_Avoid",
  "title": "The Bounty Even Hunters Avoid",
  "summary": "In Chalmun's cantina on Tatooine, a brawl erupts as the pirate Greven Sylar turns on his own thugs to help the Ortolan Frederiko, while the smuggler Wes, the knife-fighter Mayre, and the white-haired pacifist Ai'kani beat down a Trandoshan, an Aqualish, and their ringleader. Ai'kani spares the antagonists and preaches against needless killing, and the Quarren swordsman Thrask, who fights crime as a general, quietly watches over her, giving only his first name Barrien. As the survivors share drinks, two bounty hunters, Staus and Nesin, identify Thrask from their scanner and open fire to claim the Imperial bounty on his head. In the ensuing gunfight Greven, Wes, and Thrask cut the hunters down, stunning and wounding both. Greven and Wes agree to haul the captured pair to Corellia for identification and possible reward, while Thrask, refusing any part of bounty-hunting, contemptuously washes his hands of the matter and leaves.",
